\fs28 \cf0 It\'92s used in taking the secondary hard drive and add it to the main disk using LVM.\
LVM Contains -> Physical Volume -> Volume groups->Logical Volumes.\
Logical Volumes contains the partitions.\
Steps followed are \
\
		-
\fs32 > Create a physical Volume. (pvcreate /dev/sdb  and pvcreate /dev/sdc)\

\fs28 \
               -> To display the physical volume created (pvs or pvdisplay)\
